Description:

Solution_Comment__c:
Your request for providing the source code of Netwrix Access Analyzer (formerly Enterprise Auditor) can not be fulfilled.
This is because Netwrix products including Netwrix Access Analyzer (Enterprise Auditor) is not an open source software. Its source code is intellectual property of the company and can not be shared.
